# Logs Directory

This directory contains runtime logs for DataMind services.

## Log Files

- `backend.log` - Backend API server logs (FastAPI/Uvicorn)
- `frontend.log` - Frontend Next.js development server logs
- `backend.pid` - Backend process ID (created when running)
- `frontend.pid` - Frontend process ID (created when running)

## Viewing Logs

**Backend logs:**

```bash
tail -f logs/backend.log
```

**Frontend logs:**

```bash
tail -f logs/frontend.log
```

**Both logs simultaneously:**

```bash
tail -f logs/*.log
```

## Note

Log files are automatically created when you run `./start.sh` and are gitignored to keep the repository clean.
